            "code": "<div class=\"collection-slider\"><img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0585/8462/9443/files/Vaporizers-For-Sale_78c9a5a4-16d0-4dc2-8c20-5b2e6c1bcad4.jpg?v=1684209618\"  alt=\"Vaporizers For Sale\" ></a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"collection-des\">\n  <h2 class=\"collection-header\"> The Best Vaporizers Online</h2>\n  An ingenious innovation, vaporizers heat your favorite herbs or concentrates to an ideal temperature so you can enjoy the flavor and effects without combustion. We offer a variety of different styles including <a href=\"/collections/vape-pens\">vap pens</a>, <a href=\"/collections/desktop-vaporizers\">desktop vaporizers</a>, &amp; <a href=\"/collections/dab-wax-pens\">dab wax pens</a>.</div>\n<div class=\"subcat-bottom\"></div>",
